{
  "stem": "9728.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just-- don't-- it was just, it was just-- it was not pleasant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you know, people-- everyone was, hiss, oh my child, oh my thing, and the here and where's here and don't move here and-- it was just a chaos!",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a chaos as you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they let us out in certain small places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They did not let us out all the 300 in the same place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as we went along, they let us out 50 people here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In another 50 miles farther down another 50 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Another.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they insisted that the Jewish population in those other places will take us in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They let us out in a small place called Zmigrod.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Zmigrod.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was near a little, near a town called [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was, I said, in the southeastern part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Zmigrod was a very small place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was more or less like a village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I know that they let out of there probably about 40 to 50 people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They unhooked one wagon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or they opened one wagon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they let them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they ordered the Jewish community in those places, make sure that you take those people in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came to Zmigrod, they let us out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were-- they-- some Jewish committee waited for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, there was probably maybe about, maybe about 40, 50 Jewish people lived in that little place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they assigned everyone--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, well, we just did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They opened the-- they opened the doors and we had to jump down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at that time we still carried our luggage and our bedding.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't do-- they just, raus!",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
